import Layout from '../components/templates/layouts'
import { Hero } from '../components/organisms'
import {Container, Wrapper, View, Image} from '../components/atoms'
import ImageHero from '../assets/illustrations/daily-resources.svg'

const App = () => {
    
    return (
        <>
            <Layout title="Daily Resources">
                <Hero 
                title="Daily Resources" 
                subtitle="The more that you read the more things you will know." 
                img={ImageHero}/>
                <Container isEqualWidth="100%" isEqualHeight="100vh" boxSizing="border-box" padding="0px 100px 0px 100px">
                    <Wrapper>
                        <View className="half" backgroundColor="pink">
                            <View height="250" width="100%">
                                <Image src="/static/unsplash/lucas-benjamin-wQLAGv4_OYs-unsplash.jpg" width="100%" height="100%"/>
                            </View>
                        </View>
                        <View className="half" backgroundColor="lightgreen">
                            Content
                        </View>
                    </Wrapper>
                </Container>
            </Layout>
        </>
    )
}

export default App;
